================+
SQLWebProxySharp|
================+

SQLWebProxySharp will be a simple web server using the .NET HttpListener. Its sole purpose will be to proxy SQL queries over a local network to a MySQL instance running on the same server.

There is currently no security mechanism, so I strongly recommend to NOT use this over a public network.

==========+
Reasioning|
==========+

This project is written for a little Metro style application. Since Metro apps can't access MySQL servers directly, I was in need for something different to allow my Metro app the MySQL backend.

